snippet.title: Diana and Roma at Riyadh Toy Festival, Meet & Greet
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma at the Riyadh Toy Festival for a fun-filled Meet & Greet! See their adventures as they explore the festival and meet their fans. Don't miss out on this exciting event with your favorite YouTube kids!
